snippet.title: Owl City X Neural Cloud - Up To The Cloud (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Dear professors,
Neural Cloud is now available across the globe!
Neural Cloud THEME SONG by Owl City "Up to the Cloud" is out now!
When we start, we won't stop. 
Back yourself up to the cloud!
